data.description: Move in ready 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2 car garage home. Home has been totally remodeled with BRAND NEW ROOF with an added skylight in the Kitchen which brightens up the center of the home without any lights on. The kitchen is light and bright with white cabinets, granite counters and stainless steel appliances including the microwave conveniently located above the stove. The dinning area is located close to kitchen making entertaining a breeze. The formal living room is large and nicely done as soon as you walk in this lovely home. Has tile woodgrain floors that will last forever. Home has cozy family room towards the back of the home with a guest bedroom and exit to the back yard. Down the hallway you will find the guest bathroom nicely done with new shower/tub area and new toilet. The nicely sized guest bedroom is at the end of the hallway along with the large Master bedroom which has an attached bathroom and walk in closet. The laundry room is large with ample storage for pantry needs or extra appliances and a coat closet. Home also comes with washer and dryer. Home has a large 2 car garage with both sides having openers. This home sits on a large corner lot with a circular drive and a fenced in backyard for your family pet. There is also a shed that is approximately 10X10 for all your extra storage needs. Come check this home out needs nothing, close to shopping and fun things to do all around us. Crystal River, Rainbow River, Lake Hernando all waiting for you to enjoy.
